### UI-UX ACCESSIBILITY RULE (V1.0) ###

# DESIGN SYSTEM (HYBRID-BENTO)
- Background: Creme (#FFFDD0).
- Primary Text: Navy (#000080).
- Accent: Gold (#FFC72C).

# ACCESSIBILITY (WCAG 2.1 AA)
- Contrast: All text must meet a 4.5:1 ratio.
- Alt-Text: Mandatory for all images/diagrams.
- Semantic HTML: Use <h1> to <h3> hierarchy; avoid bolding for headers.

### END RULE-SET ###
